    @template theme_apsolu/components/navigation-menu

    Template Moodle pour afficher la navbar custom sur la page d'accueil.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * nav_link_1_url
    * nav_link_2_url
    * nav_link_3_url
    * nav_link_1_text
    * nav_link_2_text
    * nav_link_3_text
    * output - The core renderer for the page

    Example context (json):
    {
        "output": {
            "nav_link_1_url": true,
            "theme_apsolu/nav_link_1_text": "",
            "nav_link_2_url": "",
            "theme_apsolu/nav_link_2_text": "",
            "nav_link_3_url": "",
            "theme_apsolu/nav_link_3_text": "",
            "support_contact": "",
        },
        "config": {
            "wwwroot": "#"
        },
        "sitename": "Moodle Site"
    }
}}
    <ul class="nav mr-auto apsolu-link-light">
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="{{{ output.nav_link_1_url }}}">{{{ output.nav_link_1_text }}}</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="{{{ output.nav_link_2_url }}}">{{{ output.nav_link_2_text }}}</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="{{{ output.nav_link_3_url }}}">{{{ output.nav_link_3_text }}}</a>
        </li>
    </ul>
